    "StartAFK": {
        "action": {
            "type": "Custom",
            "param": {
                "custom_action": "StartAFKAction"
            }
        },
        "$comment": "AFK全自动运营入口。由 AgentServer 的 schedule 循环持续调度，\n此处 Pipeline 节点仅作为 tasker.run_task() 的入口锚点，\n实际调度逻辑由 scheduler.py 控制。",
        "next": [
            "[JumpBack]GlobalGuard",
            "AFK_CheckDaily",
            "AFK_CheckRadar",
            "AFK_CheckMerge",
            "AFK_CheckExpedition"
        ],
        "$__mpe_code": {
            "position": {
                "x": 252,
                "y": 501
            }
        }
    },
    "AFK_CheckDaily": {
        "recognition": {
            "type": "Custom",
            "param": {
                "custom_recognition": "DailyStatusChecker"
            }
        },
        "$comment": "检查今日任务是否完成（捐赠/科研/岛屿大作战）。\n通过 CustomRecognition 读取 StateManager 中的 tasks.donated 等标记。",
        "next": [
            "[JumpBack]GlobalGuard",
            "StartDailyTasks"
        ],
        "$__mpe_code": {
            "position": {
                "x": 572,
                "y": 149
            }
        }
    },
    "AFK_CheckRadar": {
        "recognition": {
            "type": "Custom",
            "param": {
                "custom_recognition": "RadarReadyChecker"
            }
        },
